ore rap mainstream scene, after Puff Daddy and Bad Boy Entertainment briefly dominated the charts with their pop-orientated and sample-reliant songs. <a href=\"https://www.last.fm/music/DMX/It%27s+Dark+And+Hell+Is+Hot\">Read more on Last.fm</a>. User-contributed text is available under the Creative Commons By-SA License; additional terms may apply."}}}